{{flavour|Summons some of the greater threats from one of the Pits of Slime, the Elven Halls, the Vaults, the Crypt, the Tomb of Ancients, or the Realm of Zot; the specific branch varies with each cast of the spell.}}

'''Plane Rend''' is a monster-only spell which summons 1-3 monsters from one of the following randomly selected [[branch]]es, with each branch being of equal likelihood. Its summon cap is 6.

